    - rid: 107151358184390668
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390669
          - rid: 107151358184390670
          output: 'The people gather around the pyre with heavy hearts. The accused''s
            cries for mercy fall upon deaf ears, yet he maintained his innocence
            until his final breath. The populace is disturbed, questioning why we
            would consign one of our own to the flames.

            [Lost 10 Zeal
            & 5 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 45
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390671
          - rid: 107151358184390672
          output: 'The people rejoice! The shrieks of a heretic are as music to the
            ears of the masses. The burning of a transgressor always serves to rouse
            the spirit... and keep dissidents at bay.

            [Gained 10 Zeal
            & 10 Bliss]

'
        - weight: 5
          module:
          - rid: 107151358184390673
          output: 'What calamity! What horror! We are surely forsaken! As we bound
            the cleric to the stake, he remained defiant, simply whispering "Forgive
            them, Father, for they know not what they do" while gazing at the sky.
            He did not flinch as the flames rose, and when the fire died out, his
            body had vanished! The people believe we have slain a scion of the Beholder!

            [Lost
            50 Zeal Gained Bane]

'
